IMAPAccount mailbox
Host imap.mailbox.org
Port 993
User v.narouie@mailbox.org
PassCmd "pass show mail/mailbox.org/imap | head -n 1"
TLSType IMAPS
AuthMechs LOGIN
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore mailbox-remote
Account mailbox

MaildirStore mailbox-local
SubFolders Verbatim
Path ~/Mail/
Inbox ~/Mail/INBOX

Channel mailbox
Far :mailbox-remote:
Near :mailbox-local:
Patterns *
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *
Sync All
